-75,-210,-210,-217,-222,-223,-220,-227,-227,-230,-230,-230,-230,-1914,-2398]
Now, we shall see how Magnus Carlsen himself fell victim of Black's
restricting strategy. In the line} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. a3 Bxc3+ 5.
bxc3 {Black played} c5 6. e3 Nc6 {which is considered to be the traditional
