[%csl Rc4,Gc5,Rd3,Gd6,Re3,Re4,Gf5,Rg3,Gg6][%cal Gd8d7,Ge8f6,Gc6a5,Ga8e8]
Remember this pawn constellation. The pawn chains h7-g6-f5 and d6-c5 manage to
kill all white minor pieces. At the same time, White should care about the
